"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-3fb9b3c elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"3fb9b3c\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-cc88e83\" data-id=\"cc88e83\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8fa06ee elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8fa06ee\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Acute Respiratory Distress Syndrome (ARDS)<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-64ba26a elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"64ba26a\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-2c8d023\" data-id=\"2c8d023\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-05c8ae9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"05c8ae9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Berlin Criteria<\/strong> <a class=\"button\" style=\"background-color: #193556; padding: 2px 7px; border-radius: 2px;\" href=\"#MN\">Mn <\/a><\/p><ul><li>Bilateral Opacities on Imaging<\/li><li>Acute Onset &lt; 7 Days<\/li><li>PaO2:FiO2 &lt; 300<\/li><li>Not <strong>Fully<\/strong> Explained by CHF or Fluid Overload<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Severity<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>*Based on PaO2:FiO2 (P:F Ratio)<\/li><li>Mild: P:F &lt; 300<\/li><li>Moderate: P:F &lt; 200<\/li><li>Severe: P:F &lt; 100<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Mortality<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Overall High Mortality (40%)<\/li><li>Increases with Disease Severity<ul><li>Mild: 35%<\/li><li>Moderate: 40%<\/li><li>Severe: 46%<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Causes<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Sepsis (Most Common Cause)<\/li><li>Pneumonia (Most Common Community-Acquired Cause)<\/li><li>Aspiration<\/li><li>Trauma<\/li><li>Massive Transfusion\/Transfusion-Related Acute Lung Injury (TRALI)<\/li><li>Pancreatitis<\/li><li>Inhalation Injury<\/li><li>Cardiothoracic Surgery<\/li><li>Medications<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Presentation<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Dyspnea<\/li><li>Altered Mental Status<\/li><li>Respiratory Distress<\/li><li>Complications:<ul><li>Impaired Gas Exchange &amp; Hypoxemia<ul><li>Most Common Long-Term Defect: Decreased <strong>Diffusion Capacity<\/strong><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Decreased Lung Compliance<\/li><li>Barotrauma<\/li><li>Pulmonary Hypertension<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Phases<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>1<sup>st<\/sup> Phase: <em>Exudative Phase<\/em><ul><li>Diffuse Alveolar Damage (DAD) Over the First 7-10 Days<\/li><li>Effects:<ul><li>Necrosis &amp; Sloughing of Type I Pneumocytes &amp; Capillary Endothelium<ul><li>Loss of Tight Junctions that Prevent Fluid Movement<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><strong>Inflammatory Exudate (Protein Rich) Floods Alveoli<\/strong> \u2013 From Increased Vascular Permeability<\/li><li><strong>Lung Injury <\/strong>\u2013 From Leukocyte Proliferation<\/li><li>Collapse &amp; Shunting \u2013 From Surfactant Inhibition<\/li><li>Hyaline Membrane Forms within Alveoli<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>2<sup>nd<\/sup> Phase: <em>Fibroproliferative Phase<\/em><ul><li>Proliferation of Type II Pneumocytes After 7-10 Days<\/li><li>Generally Lasts About 14-21 Days<\/li><li>Effects:<ul><li>Early Collagen Formation<\/li><li>Interstitial Infiltration of Myofibroblasts<\/li><li>Decreased Compliance<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><strong>Still Reversible<\/strong><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>3<sup>rd<\/sup> Phase: <em>Fibrotic Phase<\/em><ul><li>Interstitial Fibrosis<\/li><li>Not a Universal Outcome Seen in All Patients<\/li><li>Associated with &amp; Prolonged Mechanical Ventilation &amp; Increased Mortality<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Diagnosis<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Diagnosis: Clinical Diagnosis Based on the Berlin Criteria (Above)<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-fab863a\" data-id=\"fab863a\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1842a5c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1842a5c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-10945 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/ARDS.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"418\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/ARDS.jpg 500w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/ARDS-300x251.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p><p>ARDS <sup>1<\/sup><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-ebe662d elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"ebe662d\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-01a427b\" data-id=\"01a427b\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a671c94 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a671c94\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Acute Respiratory Distress Syndrome (ARDS) \u2013 Treatment<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-4154636 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"4154636\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-93661ba\" data-id=\"93661ba\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-83e39d8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"83e39d8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Primary Treatment<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Supportive Care<ul><li>Treat Underlying Pathology<\/li><li>Conservative Fluid Management<ul><li>Improves Ventilator-Free &amp; ICU-Free Days<\/li><li><strong>No Mortality Benefit<\/strong><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Manage Patient-Ventilator Dyssynchrony<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Lung Protective Ventilation<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Lung Protective Ventilation<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Definition: Ventilation with <strong>Low Tidal Volumes<\/strong> to Reduce Alveolar Overdistention &amp; Barotrauma<\/li><li>Improves Mortality for ARDS of All Severities<\/li><li><em>Ventilation (Tidal Volume\/Respiratory Rate)<\/em><ul><li>Initially Tidal Volume: 8 ml\/kg x Ideal Body Weight (General Standard)<\/li><li>Decrease Tidal Volume 1 ml\/kg Every 1-2 Hours<\/li><li>Goal Tidal Volume: <strong>4-6 ml\/kg<\/strong> x Ideal Body Weight<\/li><li>Adjust Tidal Volume &amp; Respiratory Rate for <strong>Goal Plateau Pressure \u2264 30 cm H2O<\/strong><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Oxygenation (PEEP\/FiO2)<\/em><ul><li>Oxygenation Goals: PaO2 55-80 mmHg or SpO2 88-95%<\/li><li>Adjust PEEP to Required FiO2<\/li><li>Initially Recommended to Start with Lower-PEEP Strategy<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-12f18f1 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"12f18f1\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-6ddefe5\" data-id=\"6ddefe5\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ff83960 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ff83960\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<table style=\"border-top: 1px solid lightgrey; max-width: 500px;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"66\"><strong>FiO2<\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"46\">0.3<\/td>\n<td width=\"46\">0.4<\/td>\n<td width=\"55\">0.5<\/td>\n<td width=\"46\">0.6<\/td>\n<td width=\"64\">0.7<\/td>\n<td width=\"46\">0.8<\/td>\n<td width=\"64\">0.9<\/td>\n<td width=\"64\">1.0<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"66\"><strong>PEEP<\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"46\">5<\/td>\n<td width=\"46\">5-8<\/td>\n<td width=\"55\">8-10<\/td>\n<td width=\"46\">10<\/td>\n<td width=\"64\">10-14<\/td>\n<td width=\"46\">14<\/td>\n<td width=\"64\">14-18<\/td>\n<td width=\"64\">18-24<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-cc10ca0 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"cc10ca0\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-4cebef4\" data-id=\"4cebef4\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d6dc92a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d6dc92a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<ul><li style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><ul><li>Consider High-PEEP Strategy if Refractory<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-4cd34ea elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"4cd34ea\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-02d50d8\" data-id=\"02d50d8\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-10d600a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"10d600a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<table style=\"border-top: 1px solid lightgrey; max-width: 500px;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"66\"><strong>FiO2<\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"55\">0.3<\/td>\n<td width=\"64\">0.4<\/td>\n<td width=\"64\">0.5<\/td>\n<td width=\"73\">0.6-0.7<\/td>\n<td width=\"73\">0.8-0.9<\/td>\n<td width=\"64\">1.0<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"66\"><strong>PEEP<\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"55\">5-14<\/td>\n<td width=\"64\">14-16<\/td>\n<td width=\"64\">16-18<\/td>\n<td width=\"73\">20<\/td>\n<td width=\"73\">22<\/td>\n<td width=\"64\">22-24<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-e8adb33 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"e8adb33\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-8fb777a\" data-id=\"8fb777a\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-aa2a4b2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"aa2a4b2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<ul><li>Complications:<ul><li><strong><em>Permissive Hypercapnia<\/em><\/strong><ul><li>Respiratory Acidosis Allowed to Maintain Low Tidal Volumes<\/li><li>PaCO2 Goal Not Well Defined<\/li><li>Should Generally Maintain pH 7.25-7.50<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Patient-Ventilator Dyssynchrony<\/em><ul><li>May Require Increased Sedation<\/li><li><a href=\"http:\/\/operativereview.com\/mechanical-ventilation-patient-ventilator-dyssynchrony\/\">*See Surgical Critical Care: Mechanical Ventilation \u2013 Patient-Ventilator Dyssynchrony<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Ancillary Measures<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><em>Prone Positioning<\/em><ul><li><strong>Mortality Benefit for Moderate-Severe ARDS<\/strong><ul><li>No Mortality Benefit for Mild ARDS<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><a href=\"http:\/\/operativereview.com\/mechanical-ventilation-ventilator-management\/\">*See Surgical Critical Care: Mechanical Ventilation \u2013 Ventilator Management<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Inhaled Vasodilators (Nitric Oxide\/Prostacyclin)<\/em><ul><li>Improves Oxygenation but No Proven Morbidity\/Mortality Benefit<\/li><li><a href=\"http:\/\/operativereview.com\/mechanical-ventilation-ventilator-management\/\">*See Surgical Critical Care: Mechanical Ventilation \u2013 Ventilator Management<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Paralysis\/Neuromuscular Blockade<\/em><ul><li>Early Short-Term (48 Hour) Paralytics May Improve Mortality in Severe ARDS (Debated with Conflicting Results)<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Extracorporeal Membrane Oxygenation (ECMO)<\/em><ul><li><a href=\"http:\/\/operativereview.com\/mechanical-circulatory-support\/\">*See Surgical Critical Care: Mechanical Circulatory Support<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Alternative Modes of Ventilation:<ul><li><em>Airway Pressure Release Ventilation (APRV)<\/em><\/li><li><em>High-Frequency Oscillatory Ventilation (HFOV)<\/em><\/li><li><a href=\"http:\/\/operativereview.com\/mechanical-ventilation-settings-modes\/\">*See Surgical Critical Care: Mechanical Ventilation \u2013 Settings &amp; Modes<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-6b6c3fe elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"6b6c3fe\" data-element_type=\"section\" id=\"MN\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-2378e05\" data-id=\"2378e05\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-74b49a7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\